{"tid":164453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉棄圖書館內殘體字書   背妻偷食鄭錦滿被控盜竊周四提堂","createTime":"2017-03-20T16:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T01:29:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a86c353ff484d6511fa41dbd26d491b9fd3253f1","tid":164453,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:09:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170320/56456312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170320%2F56456312&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5SwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=ad99486a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170320%2F56456312&h=1d3b3cbb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170320/56456312</a><br />\n<br />\n「熱血賤民」公佈，該黨副主席背妻偷食鄭錦滿因早前在圖書館拍片，籲市民用「自己方式」將簡體字書下架，今日被警方拘捕帶往元朗警署，並落案控以「盜竊罪」，將於本週四(23日)在九龍城裁判院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n人稱「四眼哥哥」的熱血公民成員鄭錦滿於去年4月2日拍片，示範在公共圖書館搜集簡體字書籍並將其銷毀，包括在隱蔽處扔掉，如放在消防喉隱蔽地方、垃圾桶及圖書館書櫃與牆壁間空隙中，涉及書籍逾20本。去年4月他曾被警方網絡安全及科技罪案組人員拘捕，涉觸犯不誠實使用電腦及盜竊罪。"},{"pid":"8540906dc78ac18f7fe7f6d48b144dac27b85c16","tid":164453,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"冇成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b5c67b90c1b20a1163eb43e3f1c859c747c049","tid":164453,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:18:08.000Z","msg":"又食熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拎左兩席仲要攞彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1710c73e050b42a398b8f9783cfb24ca8d2d68","tid":164453,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:21:52.000Z","msg":"咁都可以屈盜竊?<br />\n<br />\n咁以後去圖書館拎本書冇放返原位咪又係盜竊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{